caption: The quesataco is so good. Put everything that comes on the tray on the tacos! The flavors are so fresh and tasty!
The quesatacos were in my top 5 tacos ever had..holy smokes the flavor is potently amazing.

The food was really good. The service was extremely rude. I visited last Tuesday and simply asked the gentleman behind the counter if the tortillas were corn/gluten free.  He gave me a dirty look and responded ignorantly stating he can’t guarantee anything. So he didn’t even answer the question I asked.  I think the owner needs to make sure the staff have better manners and learn how to answer questions without an attitude.
Got the birria tacos. They are done well. Comes with three, which is good to share. Plenty of sauces in the side.

Muchachas at Armature works food hall did not disappoint. Finally tried their street tacos which were very tasty just needed to be a bit more hot (not spicy, heat hot). However their queso tacos were out of this world. Made to order, fried cheese and pulled beef tacos with a smoky tomato sauce for dipping. A side of beans and a pineapple Jarritos and you can’t go wrong. Bien tasty. Will definitely recommend and visit again.

Finally got to try the quesa tacos here. So good. But I wish they made them al pastor too. Street corn was different but had great flavor. A bit pricey for just 3 tacos but hey they were fresh and taste great.
Great place for those trendy tacos dipped in the sauce! The street pork tacos were also amazing! Can't wait to visit again with the whole family!
Food was really good. The kids loved it.
This place is top notch. Truly great MX food. Los Quesabirrias are to die for...... so good.

Biiiiiirrrrrrrra! Muchachas calls them Quesatacos, but nevertheless they are delish! For about $13 you can get three of these tacos with that are stuffed with beef and cheese with extra beef consume to dip with on the side. These really hit the spot and are full of flavor. This what they are known for so definitely gotta try them!  It's located within the Armature Works complex with plenty of other establishments as well. This place stands out with its retro modern design and easy and quick service. Their salsas are really yummy too. Grab one or two extras just incase!

Quesotacos deserve a 5 star review and worth every penny. My husband said “the only good food I’ve ever had at armature works”- and we have eaten at graze, pizza, bbq, and ramen. Not much to say except that the quesabirria had delicious fatty beef (in a good way), yummy consume to dip, and the salsas were to die for. Order it, it’s delicious. I will probably try their other menu items soon too (churros and corn).

Had the opportunity to visit this gem last Thursday and what an amazing experience! These are the best street tacos in the Bay!! The diping sauce is the kicker! OMG...this place is my new spot for Taco Tuesday!! 🌮 Great Staff as well Love it!!
Great food... easily one of my top spots for a good taco
Best Taco Ever; not only the taste, the "mess" of eating them was fun!

The BEST beef quesabirria I’ve tasted thus far! You get 3 hefty filled and fried to perfection tacos with a side of beef consomé that just adds a plethora of flavors all at once. I went back twice in one week because I couldn’t get enough. The location is great since it right inside of armature works. I’m hoping they open up other locations. I also tried the burrito and it was HUGE and delicious. It would be nice to see them do taco Tuesday deals as well. Overall, won me over. I’ll definitely be back.
THIS IS THE BEST RESTAURANT AT ARMATURE WORKS!!! The nicest staff and the best food. Definitely head over to Muchachas if you make the trip to Armature works!!!!!
The best Quesatacos in Tampa! The staff is friendly and service is awesome! Definitely make this a stop when visiting Armature Works!

I ordered the quesatacos and the steak street tacos. While the quesatacos were good the street tacos were mediocre at best. The meat was salty and not like the steak you see at authentic taco places (It was more of a shredded beef consistency). The corn tortilla was also thin and cold. Each taco cost over 4 dollars which is very overpriced in my opinion. They also charge extra for sauce.  I probably will not return.
Sooooooo good!! The quesatacos were the best food I've ever had out. WOW! We want to hug the creator of these! :)
Best place to eat at in Amarture Works hands down!! Had the Queso tacos and they were amazing!

What a wonderful new addition to Armature Works!!! My husband and I tried the quesatacos, the street corn, a chorizo taco, and of course all the sauces! The food was absolutely delicious, fresh, and packed with loads of flavor! I highly recommend Muchachas!

Absolutely the worst! Over priced, cold, not authentic. 5 bucks for so called street corn that taste like corn I use to eat in elementary lunch cafeteria! I watched customers facail expression while eating their puchase and it was the same disappointment.
Awesome street tacos and excellent customer service!  Definitely worth going back! 🌮
The quesabirria tacos are the best I had in Tampa. Good portion for a good price
5+ Stars . We can be back twice during our stay just to get their quesatacos. The line is always long because they truly are the best. Don’t contemplate, just go here.
The quesabirra tacos were amazing!  The street corn...holy Hannah. Add chorizo to the corn for that extra flavor. Service, food, everything was 5 stars!!!

So delicious, the queso tacos are insane. They come with this amazing sauce to dip them in. The size of the queso tacos is great for the price and flavor is on point! I can't wait to try a burrito and the churros!!!

Stephanie, the owner, is amazing, the food is amazing, and the people who work there are kind and welcome your business. I was able to try the quesatacos (fan favorite) and street corn and I will 100% be back to try everything else out on the menu.
Food was 🔥.  Quesataco, salsa, churros, sauces...everything was super flavorful. Love the overall vibe of the place & staff was super friendly. Muchachas is a great addition to Armature Works.

Tampa has been needing some good Quesatacos and muchachas has done it! Perfect location inside armature works makes it easy and convenient for the whole family. Get the rice and beans too! You can taste the time effort and love that went into the recipes!

The food is absolutely excellent. The quesatacos are delicious! The carnitas tacos were to die for. The staff was very kind and attentive while taking our larger that usual order.  We will definitely be back.  Stephanie Swanz of Empamamas has solidified herself as one of the top young concept entrepreneurs in the restaurant industry. Everything she touches is quality. What a great addition to the Armature Works space.
Dipping  sauce that comes with the Quesabirria tacos is fabulous. All the salsas are above par. Street corn is delicious and a  good deal at five dollars.
Loving this place, so excited to see them join armature works. Try the street corn and quesabirra tacos!

From the beautiful pops of color that make up Muchachas exterior to the enticing aroma as you walk up, your senses are in for a treat! What an amazing dinner experience at Muchachas! I had never had a quesataco before and I can’t wait to have more. The meat is so juicy and tender it just melts in your mouth. My husband ordered the the big ole burrito and wow!! You might think it’s just a burrito but no, this was art. The rice was perfectly cooked, the corn salsa was slightly sweet so it complimented the perfect saltiness of the also tender meat and all in all was just a big ole helping of amazing. I can’t wait to go back and try the street corn and churros. Thank you Muchachas for a great experience!!

Where do I even begin!! The quesabirria tacos are hands down the best you’ll ever have. The burrito was also fantastic. I’m very picky about guac and it was perfect. And do nothing DARE not get that street corn. It was just all so good, and the space is adorable... this place is gonna kill it.
Freaking Amazing!!!! You must try the QuesaTacos.... out of this world!!!! Staff are awesome and super friendly. Can't wait to try the Big Ole Burrito!!!!
The quesatacos are absolutely delicious!!! The street corn is amazing!!! Great staff!!!

Hands down the best quesatacos I've ever had, no exaggeration. The meat was melt-in-your-mouth tender and the cheese was so perfectly gooey with just the right amount of crisping on the sneaky edges that spilled out of the tortilla. All 3 sauces are so well balanced that it's almost impossible to choose a favorite to dip in (but the beef consomé is definitely a must). Next time you're at Armature Works, Muchachas is the place to go!
Had a steak burrito and absolutely loved it ! Healthy and filling portion size that left my stomach full and happy. Great atmosphere with very friendly staff and quick service. I will be back .
Everything was so delicious! I’m definitely getting thr big burrito next time!
Loved everything about these tacos. Will be eating these very often. The street corn was delicious as well.
Had the quesatacos and washed it down with a Mexican coca-cola! 🤤 Make sure to give this place a try next time at Armature Works!!
Delicious tacos and street corn 🤤 This will be my go-to anytime I want mexican street food in Tampa !

Wow! Once I heard burritos I was beyond excited to try Muchachas. I got the Carne burrito which was tasteful and authentic. The steak was cut perfectly, nothing is worse than big chunks of tough steak in your burrito. Not only was the food tasty but the customer service was friendly and welcoming. 100% coming back for more. Next must try are the Quesatacos.
